This paper proposes a novel knowledge graph embedding model that aims to model semantic hierarchies in knowledge graphs. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Databases (cs.DB).
